- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper mentions the use of FrameNet, which is a machine learning-based approach to frame semantics. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possibility as the paper deals with semantic representation and mapping, which can be relevant to information retrieval tasks. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper proposes an extension to the GF library, which can be seen as a software engineering task.
